From: Scott Hurd <shurd@aphis.usda.gov>

I agree it usually takes a multitude of untoward events for an outbreak.
It is a multivariate problem. I was interested that your final comment
mentioned the role and responsibility of the farmer/producer. What would
be your weighting factor for that variable [on farm of the equation
describing the factors involved?
Enjoying holiday dinners...,
